div.div:
Event LOG will have a set of predefined events that may happen in a game and will let the BE and FE to replay whatever happened in the game from the beginning. Therefore we are defining some events that are already defined in the product definition.
RECRUITED_UNIT (USER_ID, UNIT_ID, LOCATION) => (UNIT_INSTANCE_ID,EVENT_ID)
UNIT_MOVE(UNIT_INSTANCE_ID, MOVE_FROM, MOVE_TO) => EVENT_ID
UNIT_ATTACK(UNIT_INSTANCE_1, UNIT_INSTANCE_2, LOCATION_TO) => EVENT_ID
TOWER_ATTACK(UNIT_INSTANCE, TOWER, LOCATION_TO) => EVENT_ID
UNIT_DEAD(UNIT_INSTANCE) => EVENT_ID
TOWER_DEAD(TOWER_INSTANCE) => EVENT_ID
